      "content": "wait really? i've heard it's just an herb and basically works like a natural version of what i'm already taking. i'm not looking to do anything crazy, just a little extra support because i'm so stressed. surely a little bit won't actually cause a life-threatening emergency? it seems like a lot of drama for just a supplement.",
